{"id":144180,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/清华百年校庆-“一井一人”防投毒/","date":"2011-04-11T17:00:13Z","modified":"2011-04-11T21:52:05Z","title":"清华百年校庆 “一井一人”防投毒","content":"<p>bonnae1982 写道 &#8220;据《新京报》报道，北京清华大学将在本月 24日庆祝百周年校庆，届时中共领导人将亲赴校园参加校庆活动，北京市水务局为防有人投毒、破坏供水设施，已派专人守清华自备井，同时加强食水检测。 　据介绍，清华饮用水供应主要来自自备井。日前北京市水务局供水处与市节水管理中心对清华大学百年校庆期间，自备井安全供水保障的情况进行了检查。市水务局相关负责人表示，清华百年校庆期间，为保证供水水质合格将加强水质监测工作，首先是校庆前对供水水质进行检测，确保水质达到《生活饮用水标准》。其次，校庆期间将启动供水巡视，做好防破坏、防投毒工作。对自备井实行“一井一人”专人值守负责制。<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/14181ad5/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E6%B8%85%E5%8D%8E%E7%99%BE%E5%B9%B4%E6%A0%A1%E5%BA%86+%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%95%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%BA%E2%80%9D%E9%98%B2%E6%8A%95%E6%AF%92&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fsociety.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F04%2F11%2F0940232%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E6%B8%85%E5%8D%8E%E7%99%BE%E5%B9%B4%E6%A0%A1%E5%BA%86+%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%95%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%BA%E2%80%9D%E9%98%B2%E6%8A%95%E6%AF%92&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fsociety.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F04%2F11%2F0940232%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/98748080170/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14181ad5/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/98748080170/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14181ad5/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=ZPgfiNBomvg:_VHGm9FT_Mk:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=ZPgfiNBomvg:_VHGm9FT_Mk:7Q72WNTAKB